            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M5.583 7.229C3.119 7.224-.172 8.786.01 12.708c.281 6.125 6.557 6.693 9.068 6.745.271 1.146 3.224 5.109 5.411 5.318h9.573c5.74-.38 10.036-17.365 6.854-17.427-5.271.25-8.396.375-11.073.396v5.297l-.839-.365-.005-4.932c-3.073 0-5.781-.141-10.917-.396-.646-.005-1.542-.115-2.5-.115zm.344 2.167h.297c.349 3.141.917 4.974 2.068 7.781-2.938-.349-5.432-1.198-5.891-4.38-.24-1.646.563-3.365 3.526-3.401m11.412 3.083c.198.005.406.042.594.13l1 .432-.714 1.302a1 1 0 0 0-.323.052c-.464.151-.708.604-.542 1.021a.8.8 0 0 0 .151.229l-1.234 2.25a.8.8 0 0 0-.297.052c-.464.146-.708.604-.542 1.016.172.417.682.63 1.151.479.464-.146.703-.604.536-1.021a.8.8 0 0 0-.208-.292l1.203-2.188c.13.01.26 0 .391-.042a.8.8 0 0 0 .281-.151c.464.198.844.354 1.12.49.406.203.552.339.599.49.042.146-.005.427-.24.922-.172.37-.458.896-.797 1.51-.115 0-.229.016-.333.052-.469.151-.708.604-.542 1.021.167.411.682.625 1.146.479.469-.151.708-.604.542-1.021a.9.9 0 0 0-.182-.271c.333-.609.62-1.135.807-1.526.25-.536.38-.938.266-1.323s-.469-.635-.932-.865c-.307-.151-.693-.313-1.146-.505q.01-.163-.052-.318c-.062-.155-.109-.198-.193-.281l.703-1.281 3.901 1.682c.703.307.995 1.057.651 1.682l-2.682 4.906c-.339.625-1.182.885-1.885.578l-5.516-2.38c-.703-.307-.995-1.057-.656-1.682l2.682-4.906c.234-.432.708-.688 1.208-.708h.083z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3>Gitea</h3>
              <p>
                Connect to your Gitea instances for lightweight Git hosting.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
